author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the Ayn Thor. I bought this because I wanted to relive a little bit of the DS and 3DS and up my emulation game and I'm glad to say in the week I've been using it, it might have beaten the Steam Deck for me! Thanks for watching!

title: IT FINALLY ARRIVED
